I have a Flask-based e-commerce project called "Shopwave" with features similar to Meesho (multi-vendor marketplace, product variants, cart, orders, returns, referral system).

The backend is already well-structured, but the frontend UI/UX, styling, and template structure are poor and need a complete redesign.

Your task:
Redesign the entire frontend to match a modern, clean, mobile-first marketplace experience similar to Meesho.

Requirements:

1. UI/UX Improvements
- Clean, minimal, modern design
- Mobile-first responsive layout
- Smooth spacing, consistent typography, proper alignment
- Use professional color palette (primary + accent)
- Add skeleton loading, hover effects, and subtle animations

