- Navbar with search + categories + icons
- Product cards (discount badge, rating, free delivery)
- Buttons (primary, secondary, outline)
- Forms (clean inputs, validation UI)
- Cards and sections with proper shadows and spacing

4. Tech Stack
- Use Bootstrap 5 OR Tailwind CSS (prefer Tailwind for modern look)
- Use reusable components (Jinja templates or partials)
- Clean HTML structure with semantic tags

5. Structure Improvements
- Refactor templates into reusable components:
  - components/navbar.html
  - components/product_card.html
  - components/footer.html
- Maintain consistent layout using base.html

6. Meesho-style Features
- Sticky bottom "Buy Now" button on mobile
- Horizontal scroll categories
- Banner carousel
- Deal sections
- Clean product grid like Meesho

7. Output Format
- Provide full HTML templates
- Include CSS (or Tailwind classes)
- Include small JS if needed (for interactivity)
- Keep code clean and production-ready

Goal:
Make the UI look like a modern Indian marketplace app (similar to Meesho, Flipkart, or Amazon), not a basic Flask project.

